Class Student

java.lang.Object
models.User
models.Student
Direct Known Subclasses:
CommitteeMember
public class Student extends User
The Student class represents a student in CAMs. Student have a unique ID, password, name, and faculty. Each student also has a Role which determines their level of access.
Since:
1.0
Version:

    • Student

      public Student(String userID, String password, String name, String faculty, ArrayList<String> registeredCamps, Map<String,ArrayList<Integer>> enquiries)
      Constructor used for importing Student from CSV.
      Parameters:
      userID - The user ID of the Student member.
      password - The password of the Student member.
      name - The name of the Student member.
      faculty - The faculty to which the Student member belongs.
      registeredCamps - The list of camps the Committee Member is registered for.
      enquiries - A map containing the Committee Member's enquiries, with camp names as keys and lists of enquiry IDs as values.
